{"id": 59371, "date": "2025-08-19T04:00:35", "date_gmt": "2025-08-19T11:00:35", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=59371"}, "modified": "2026-05-13T16:55:24", "modified_gmt": "2026-05-13T23:55:24", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-august-19-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/08/19/kingdom-of-days-august-19-2/", "title": {"rendered": "August 19"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1978:\u00a0</strong>Bruce debuts his cover of &#8220;Good Rockin&#8217; Tonight&#8221; to open Night Two at the Philadelphia Spectrum on the Darkness Tour. Gary Busey guest stars on &#8220;Rave On.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/XRS3x3_mdys?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/oSNz8UoUD4s?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1983:\u00a0</strong>Bruce guest stars with John Eddie at the Brighton Bar in Long Branch, New Jersey, for a mini-set of covers, including &#8220;Blue Suede Shoes&#8221; and &#8220;Ain&#8217;t That Lovin&#8217; You Baby.&#8221;</p>\n<div id=\"v-rAT8zq3b-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='568' src='https://videopress.com/embed/rAT8zq3b?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>1984:\u00a0</strong>The penultimate night of Bruce&#8217;s ten-night Born in the U.S.A. Tour stand at East Rutherford&#8217;s Brendan Byrne Arena brings the U.S. debut of &#8220;My Father&#8217;s House&#8221; and the return of the Miami Horns for &#8220;Tenth Avenue Freeze-Out,&#8221; &#8220;Detroit Medley&#8221; and &#8220;Twist and Shout.&#8221; &#8220;Reason to Believe&#8221; is recorded and released on the <em>Live 1975-85</em> box set. This show is available as part of Bruce&#8217;s official archive series.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/-k2QcB6bV9o?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/FevxkHIymKc?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"28710\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1984-08-19/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1984-08-19.jpg?fit=926%2C983&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"926,983\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1984-08-19\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1984-08-19.jpg?fit=758%2C805&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-28710 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1984-08-19.jpg?resize=758%2C805&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"805\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1984-08-19.jpg?w=926&amp;ssl=1 926w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1984-08-19.jpg?resize=283%2C300&amp;ssl=1 283w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1984-08-19.jpg?resize=768%2C815&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1985:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band play their second of a four-night stand at Giants Stadium (they will return later that summer). The show is notable for its performances of &#8220;Johnny 99,&#8221; &#8220;Working on the Highway,&#8221; &#8220;I&#8217;m on Fire,&#8221; and &#8220;Born to Run,&#8221; all of which are recorded and will be released on the <em>Live 1975-85\u00a0</em>box set. Their &#8220;Born to Run&#8221; performance will become the audio for the official video for the song.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/IxuThNgl3YA?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/0tc6rMoyKks?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/rJVx6Ti8sJw?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpa